The Palos Verdes Art Center has announced winners of its Annual High School 
Juried Art Show. First- and second-place winners in various categories were 
announced by Andrew Seymour, principal of Miraleste High School, and Michael 
Escalante, principal of Rolling Hills High School. First and second place 
winners in each category are: 
