<TEXT>
<P>
Orion Pictures Corp.: The New York-based movie company announced net income of 
$15.1 million for the year ended Feb. 28, an increase of 8% from net income of 
$13.9 million the year before. Revenue was $485.2 million, up 3.5% from $468.9 
million in the preceding year. The company didn't elaborate on the results. 
