UNITED STATES -- BORDERS -- MEXICO; BORDER PATROL (U.S.); UNITED STATES -- 
IMMIGRATION; DRUGS -- UNITED STATES; DRUG TRAFFICKING -- MEXICO; LAW 
ENFORCEMENT 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
