Photo, Victory with D -- Dennis Rodman signals another win for the Detroit 
Pistons, who shut down the New York Knicks, 95-84, Tuesday night to clinch 
Eastern Conference playoff series, four games to one. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
