six-acre site of proosed sewage-treatment plant, left center, which has become 
entangled in a nasty legal battle. BRIAN GADBERY / Los Angeles Times; Map, 
Malibu, Los Angeles Times ; Photo, Merritt Adamson, Jr. 
</P>
