polished 1952 Pontiac. JAMES RUEBSAMEN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Even the 
interior of the classic car, including the dashboard, is kept in immaculate 
condition. ; Photo, Joan and Bernie Hackett sport their club jackets to 
advertise the upcoming car meet in Ventura. ; Photo, COLOR, (COVER) Hood 
ornament from Pontiac. 
